description: Care home matron Sue Fleming says she feels "privileged" to be the first to receive the jab.
title: Covid: First Guernsey residents vaccinated against virus
title_page: Covid: First Guernsey residents vaccinated against virus - BBC News
maintext: "We have a duty of care to the people we look after so for me there was no choice at all. It's really important that we all do this," she said.
